text: Sufa or SUFA may refer to: *Sufa, Israel, a kibbutz in Israel and a border crossing between Israel and the Gaza Strip *Sufa, Sinai, a former Israeli settlement in Sinai *AIL Storm, also known as Sufa, an Israel Defense Forces vehicle *INS Sufa, an Israeli Sea Corps Saar 4.5 class missile boat *Social Union Framework Agreement, a Canadian labour agreement
title: Sufa
